{
  "stem": "15694.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First there were like long boards and three tiers, and we slept at the top tier.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were working in the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I found in later camps, wherever you went, newcomers always got the worst.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at this particular stretch, it was good old Amon Goeth, we called him 'Get,' a commandant of Plaszow, who-- his villa wasn't far away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when he went-- when he got up-- I'm not sure whether that was before breakfast or after, but it was some kind of a morning exercise, he looked through the-- through his telescope.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had a rifle with a telescope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If somebody idled or rested a minute on his pick axe or shovel, he would be shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That would soon make sure that all the others worked until they would drop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At that time, I developed something which I already discussed with my father, all systems go for survival.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Don't be conspicuous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And whatever you do, everything has to be sort of worked out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And to work that way and the food we got, I'm sure we wouldn't have lasted long.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You would have to take a rest, and that was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I did, I put the shovel into the ground, but I expected that somebody would see me moving.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the important thing, don't stand still.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And took the almost empty shovel out and with the movement as if I had, you know, done the work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I worked with my eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I looked and all around, and looked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, if somebody would come near who looked suspicious to me, as either a guard or one of the Germans, of course I could work harder.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
